We collect and generate the following types of personal data concerning users of our Platform -user account information (email address and, when applicable, hashed password);profile and contact information (name, title, team, company, email and phone number, and additional information and media submitted by them, their teammates or their organization);
We collect data from your electronic messages (email) that are ONLY related to messages to prospects in objects in Customer Relationship Management tools, and we do not share this data.
We collect such data either automatically, through the data subject's interaction with us or with our website, Platform or Services; or through third party services, social media, analytics tools, events we organize or participate in, and other business initiatives.
